## 📱 RESPONSIVE BEHAVIOR

| Breakpoint | Width | Behavior |
|------------|-------|----------|
| `xs` | < 480px | Single column, reduced animations |
| `sm` | 480–768px | Single column, full animations |
| `md` | 768–1024px | 2-column grid begins |
| `lg` | 1024–1280px | Full layout, sidebar appears |
| `xl` | 1280–1536px | Max content width cap |
| `2xl` | > 1536px | Ultra-wide: center-lock content |

- All font sizes use `clamp()` for fluid scaling.
- Navigation collapses to hamburger at `< 768px`.
- Session overlay stacks vertically on mobile.
- Reduce motion: wrap all Framer Motion animations in:
  ```typescript
  const prefersReducedMotion = window.matchMedia('(prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)').matches;
  ```

